  "response": "The cost of CATIA Specialist level certification exams can vary depending on the specific exam, location, and testing center. However, as of my last update, the typical cost for a CATIA Specialist level certification exam ranges from approximately $100 to $300 USD.\n\nTo get the most accurate and up-to-date pricing information, I recommend visiting the official Dassault Syst\u00e8mes website or contacting an authorized testing center directly. They will be able to provide you with the current fees for the specific CATIA Specialist certification you are interested in.",
